---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="About — AnyaDeals" description="Learn about AnyaDeals and our deal curation process.">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="headline-lg mb-8">About AnyaDeals</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6 text-ink-muted leading-relaxed">
      <p class="text-lg text-ink">We cut through the noise. Every deal, code, and product on AnyaDeals is verified — saving you hours and real money.</p>

      <p>AnyaDeals started as a personal project to track the best iHerb supplement deals across Europe and the Balkans. What began as a spreadsheet of promo codes turned into an automated platform that discovers, validates, and publishes verified deals daily.</p>

      <h2 class="headline-md text-ink mt-12 mb-4">How It Works</h2>

      <ol class="list-decimal list-inside space-y-3">
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Discover</strong> — Our research service scans dozens of coupon sites, forums, and social media for new promo codes.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Verify</strong> — Every code is tested automatically through real checkout flows using residential proxies across multiple countries.</li>
        <li><strong class="text-ink">Publish</strong> — Only verified, working codes make it to the site. Expired codes are flagged and removed.</li>
      </ol>

      <h2 id="disclosure" class="headline-md text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Affiliate Disclosure</h2>

      <div class="bg-white border border-border-raw/10 rounded-lg p-6">
        <p>This site contains affiliate links. When you purchase through our links, we may earn a commission at no extra cost to you. This helps us keep the site running and continue verifying deals for you.</p>
        <p class="mt-3">We use iHerb's referral program (code: OFR0296) and participate in the iHerb affiliate program via Impact. Our recommendations are based on genuine testing and verification — we only promote products and deals we believe offer real value.</p>
      </div>

      <h2 class="headline-md text-ink mt-12 mb-4">Contact</h2>
      <p>Have a deal tip or question? Reach out on <a href="#" class="text-signal hover:underline">Twitter/X</a> or <a href="#" class="text-signal hover:underline">Reddit</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
